{Partner's bid asks if you have 4 \Ss, and denies a \H stopper. (DIRECT DENIES)

You don't have 4 \Ss, nor can you stop \Hs. You have no choice but to bid one of the 4-card Minor suits, so you go up-the-line and bid 4\C. Partner bids 5\C.}

